title: Cold Spray Additive Manufacturing
description: Cold spray additive manufacturing (CSAM) is a revolutionary technology with significant importance in the realm of advanced manufacturing. Unlike traditional additive manufacturing methods, CSAM relies on supersonic gas jets to deposit functional particles at high velocities, creating dense and high-quality coatings without the need for melting or extensive post-processing.   
